snippet.textDisplay: This song, the Hindi part, sung by Sona M,  is not Sufi, though the music instrument style is certainly has Persian Sufi style.  But what is amazing is songwriters have  made this song  more then Sufi, it's a  combination of  two cultures, Hindu and Muslim, as it happened over centuries past in South Asia.  An amazing upbeat & spiritual accomplishment.
